{"about_the_game":"Master of Chess is the one and only chess career simulator.<br><br><strong>Create your character and climb the ladder</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/lifetime_career.gif?t=1735847368\" /><br><br>Play the lifetime of a chess player, from a promising young talent to a seasoned pro!<br>Start as a promising young talent and become a world-class chess master. Strive for chess immortality!<br><br><strong>Improve your chess game</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/solve_puzzles.gif?t=1735847368\" /><br><br>Develop your real-life chess skills thanks to an always-present coach following your career, challenging AI opponents, tough puzzles to solve, and an always developing opening repertoire...but beware of blunders!<br><br><strong>An intelligent AI system to improve your moves</strong><br><br>Play your dream career with the help of an AI system that will guide you in selecting the best moves, picking the right openings, outmanoeuvring and outsmarting even the best opponents!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/play_match.gif?t=1735847368\" /><br><br><strong>A management experience</strong><br><br>Deadlines, tight budgets, tournament fees, stressful games... The life of a professional chess player isn't easy, but you have all the tools at your disposal to easily manage every aspect of it.<br><br><strong>Become Master of Chess</strong><br><br>Will you make it to the top?<br>Are you ready to make your mark and become a legend?<br>The chessboard is waiting. <strong>Start a lifetime journey in Master of Chess today!</strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Candidate Master (CM)","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2248900/06fc7cc31d931f7537660827bf1ac